TOPIC: WIZPROMOTIONS

Student Builder (30):
 Entry level wizard. 

Promotion to Builder (40):
 Wizard with completed firstarea. 
 Most wizards are ranked as builders. 

Promotion to Creator (50):
 Only way to to be a Creator is to be responsible for a certain portion 
 of the muds operation. This currently includes such things as QC, LAW,
 BALANCE, TEACHER, etc. an unlimited number of these positions exist but
 only experienced and active coders will be allowed to fill them.




